Perhaps a closer look at Education would be interesting? Heres a visual impression of its distribution:

Hmm. A couple of those municipalities are way up there in this right-skewed distribution, specifically. As it stands currently, this variables has a mean of 10.98 and a standard deviation of 9.62. But since its so skewed, the median (8) is the better indicator of its center. It would be worth doing a log transformation to get a more normally distributed variable as we see below. We would definitely want to work with this transformed variable in any modeling.
